        <updateDate>2021-06-02T10:52:58Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Eliminate the Digital Divide Act</b> <b>of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to establish a program to provide funding to states for expanding access to broadband service in unserved areas. States must distribute these funds to certain broadband service providers for projects that offer a low-cost broadband service option for low-income subscribers. The bill also provides funding to carry out this program.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
